{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_14", "eventName": "慈悲燈塔", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "14-20", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "列王行跡", "storyInfo": "眾人踏上了通往通天巨塔之頂的道路，到達頂端時，天翻地轉。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$memory_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "魔王以勒什死後，我又見了他很多面。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n他留在“魔王”中的情感與經歷，與我關於他的記憶有很大差異。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我印象中的他，總是垂著頭坐在議事廳的中央，在王庭成員的吵鬧聲中不發一言。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n杜卡雷和孽茨雷認為他過於懦弱，當著他的面說黑王冠再一次選錯了繼承者。而他沒有反駁，只是看著窗外熔爐燃燒形成的濃煙出神。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "後來我才知道，以勒什是一名出色的術師和工匠，他也曾孜孜不倦地研究可以改善生活條件的法術，為卡茲戴爾如何邁進結晶時代規劃過許多可能。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n他在外遊歷多年，回到卡茲戴爾後，說服了死魂靈，準備在城市中心立起最大的熔爐。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "但隨著冠冕落在他的頭頂，新任的魔王變得越來越沉默。 ", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n陡然承受過多的情感與回憶是無比痛苦的。許多被王冠選中的人都沒來得及留下姓名，就因陷入癲狂而死去。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n而以勒什沒有墜入瘋狂，他承受住了這一切。正因為他足夠清醒，才越來越絕望。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "黑冠向他，也向我揭露了一個事實—— ", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我們所構想的，屬於薩卡茲的未來，很有可能只是薩卡茲某段歷史的重複。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n一切建造的終將歸於毀滅。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "戰爭會撕碎他的卡茲戴爾。戰爭會殺死他。", "x": 300.0, "y": 330.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n戰爭會殺死我。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g2_mainbattlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_battlefield_environment", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "bat"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warchaos_intro", "key": "$warchaos_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1341_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嘶吼）", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1341_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他快不行了！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上啊，拿下他，這巫術祭壇就廢了！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1341_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_arrow_rain", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_imp_arrow_h", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.4}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1341_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弩箭插進薩卡茲的胸膛。"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他並未在意，仍想繼續前進。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“嘀嘀”“嘀嘀”。"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他低下頭，看到插在胸口的箭羽正在發亮。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1341_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_explodebris", "volume": 0.7, "delay": 0.4}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.7}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "集束彈藥在薩卡茲的血肉中爆裂。"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一次又一次密集的爆炸，再強大的巫術都無法如此迅速地修復創傷。"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……成功了？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，真的倒了，炸沒了，只剩下骨頭渣子了！這方法真的有效，我們果然不用怕這些怪物！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等下——", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲的殘骸在發光。"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "士兵們不由得開始後退，但已經來不及了。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_skill_explocar_cast", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_explosion", "volume": 0.8, "delay": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噴薄的火光和源石粉塵吞沒了戰場一角。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"channel": "bat", "volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g3_mainbattlefield_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"channel": "bat", "volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "孽茨雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1331_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宗長！您的身體……", "name": "“靈幛”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1331_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不影響戰鬥。", "name": "孽茨雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1331_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞人，攻勢猛烈。", "name": "“靈幛”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1331_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們適應得很快……幾乎找到了對付我們的方法。", "name": "“靈幛”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1331_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的損傷正越來越大。", "name": "“靈幛”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1331_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的戰士，不會放棄。", "name": "孽茨雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的防線，仍能堅持。", "name": "孽茨雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1331_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "“靈幛”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1331_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經足夠。", "name": "孽茨雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信特雷西斯，與特蕾西婭。", "name": "孽茨雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至今……不變。", "name": "孽茨雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1339_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bat", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$memory_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "我曾很多次與特雷西斯聊起戈瀆，那位“砌城匠”。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n土石之子的氏族早已四散各地，我並不能像戈瀆一樣，號令石翼魔使用獨特的天賦，迅速地壘砌城牆。但我依然從他的堅韌性格與領導方式中獲益良多。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n織衣匠，砌城匠。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "我對特雷西斯開玩笑說，或許我和戈瀆真的很像。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n特雷西斯突然變得很嚴肅，他說，他不會讓我和戈瀆走上一樣的道路——死於最親近之人的背叛。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我無法將戈瀆的所思所感完全分享給特雷西斯。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "但戈瀆臨終時的情感深深烙印於我的腦海。他最後一眼看見的，絕不是背叛他的炎魔，而是自己與無數同胞一手建起的城市。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我們都知道，戈瀆不會是最後一位被至親至愛之人殺死的魔王，他的城市也一定不會是最後一座卡茲戴爾。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n只要仍然有人渴望回家，卡茲戴爾就一定會在灰燼中重生。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g25_wildbattlefield_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "BM和TAA兩條路目前是暢通的，可以走！在接下來的十五分鐘裡，源石晶簇還不會長過來。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I9不行，費斯特，注意信標顏色變動。附近的源石山有崩塌風險。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_1036_fang2_1#6$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——可露希爾，我們在I903偵察點！有人受傷，看起來是平民。", "name": "芬"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到了看到了，有一輛小車在路上了。注意收貨，把防具和藥拿上，它知道接下來要去哪裡。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦對，還有兩架無人機也往你們的方向去了。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "待會霧升起來之後，你看訊號燈的顏色，綠的就是前路沒問題。典範軍的人會在I901接應。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_1036_fang2_1#6$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我忍不住想……可露希爾，你這同時在操控多少雙手啊？", "name": "芬"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "可露希爾", "content": "還好，也就七八……"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "可露希爾", "content": "唔，十幾雙吧。眼睛會更多一些。"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼下的處境比絕大多數羅德島的天災救援任務都要複雜。芬……", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_1036_fang2_1#8$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，不會掉以輕心。", "name": "芬"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可露希爾，你也要……滋滋滋……", "name": "芬"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……通訊干擾？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#5$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "176和178號無人機失去訊號。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_054", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……發現物資點。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藥，吃的，都有。沒什麼能用的武器。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藥和食物可以給你一份。多的就不要拿了哦。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#10$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_054", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這赤手空拳的還能攔著……呃，血魔？", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#10$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別怕，和王庭沒關係，我也不會那種一下子抽乾你們血的法術。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#10$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_054", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呸，真要是那幫老混帳的人，我一下就射穿你的脖子！", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你們並不是來執行任務的。曼弗雷德還不會派一隊連我們的標誌都不認識的人過來。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道說這些話可能對你們沒什麼用……但這個位置馬上就要炸開了。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能不能，不要影響我工作？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_054", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃——！", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_sand", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sandstorm", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_054", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這要命的天災怎麼又要來了？王庭那幫老東西搓出來的到底是什麼東西啊，這鬼地方真是沒法待了！", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，我是467號，你們人呢？我說——", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_235", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_235", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "襲擊營地的雇傭兵均已解決。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可露希爾，走吧。該轉移到下一個安全地點了。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，謝啦，刺客大師。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_054", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "投降嗎？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "投降的話，你可以跟著我們一起走。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_054", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……都被你們抓了，那我有什麼好選的。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_235", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場仗打到現在，散落在戰場各處的雇傭兵會增多。除了聽從軍事委員會的指揮，他們還會幹回老本行。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，類似的攻擊我們還會遭遇很多次。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當年……我們不也是這麼過來的？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_235", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是啊。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是需要穿越天災，還是更多敵人……", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都會盡力讓更多想回家的人……回家。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"fade": "true", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g2_kazdelstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍事委員會是不是又有新訊息了？", "name": "薩卡茲平民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說他們剛殺了一個維多利亞大公爵，馬上就會殺第二個第三個！", "name": "薩卡茲平民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳……你那最近還有，呃，好用的藥嗎？我想治治這條傷腿，哪怕只是讓石頭稍微少一點，打起仗來跑得快一點……", "name": "薩卡茲平民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#2$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也要去倫蒂尼姆？", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#2$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆？我這哪趕得上，就算我想去，攝政王也不會要我啊。", "name": "薩卡茲平民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這場仗……早晚會打到卡茲戴爾的吧？那群維多利亞人，萊塔尼亞人……他們哪裡會這麼輕易就放過我們？", "name": "薩卡茲平民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，小個子，你也早做打算吧。再磨一磨你的兵器，回想下該怎麼殺人……", "name": "薩卡茲平民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……軍事委員會。", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#4$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多年了，我們的城市，真的又要……", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#4$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……哈……終於趕上了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，你是……", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#2$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……你的同行？", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#8$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是說信使啦！", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，一晃這麼多年過去，我對卡茲戴爾都不太熟了。我聽說啊，我能在這個座標找到我要找的人。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#6$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能告訴我——去“巴別塔”舊址的路該怎麼走嗎？", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$memory_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "巴別塔的事務進展和預期一樣阻礙重重。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我從不擔憂失敗，但我最不想看見的，就是這些心懷希望的人，再度陷入絕望的循環。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我在“魔王”中越潛越深。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "凱爾希提醒我，這可能會對我的身體造成負擔。但時間緊迫，我必須盡可能地調動所有資源。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n終於，我找到了“遠逐者”，薩卡茲的第一位魔王。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "我依稀看見一場席捲了天空與大地的戰爭，一群越來越絕望的人，還有……我無法確認那是否是源石。它的模樣和我們熟悉的黑色結晶差距很大，閃爍著一種潔淨的光澤。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我們的魔王，最初的卡茲戴爾的守衛者，將自己的鮮血與靈魂獻給了它。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n之後，永夜降臨。聲與光在我們身上消失無蹤。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "“遠逐者”放棄了留下姓名，他甚至沒有在“魔王”中留下過多情感。我想他是有意的。他代所有薩卡茲擁抱了黑暗，便也將自己埋葬在黑暗裡。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我所邁入的，是一座冷寂的墳墓。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我在墓地裡徘徊，於無聲處反覆地思索。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "直到某一刻，我意識到，黑暗中並非空無一物。", "x": 300.0, "y": 330.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "50_i19", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ghosthunter_intro", "key": "$ghosthunter_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一座塔。"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要塔建得足夠高，就能抵達我們頭頂的黑暗。"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們建起的一切固然都會崩塌毀滅，掩於流沙。"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們的意志，我們的渴求，會億萬次於塵埃中崛起。"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "攀登。"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "攀登。"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不斷地向上，越過我們的無知。"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直至，超越黑暗。"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是為什麼……這裡會有一座塔。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管怎麼樣，我們看起來總算走到頭了。", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底爬了多久？我覺得自己過了好幾輩子！", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，說不定……還要更長。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小兔子！你一直在發什麼呆？", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在聽。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……死掉的老傢伙們連詞彙量都很匱乏的嘮叨？你還沒聽膩？", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭知道自己聽見的是誰的聲音。"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "魔王就在眾魂之間。"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眾魂想讓魔王傾聽。"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭不由自主地想隨著這個聲音潛入“魔王”深處，在無數的時間與空間的碎片中摸索。"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戒指頂著她的掌心。"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要解開它們……她就能讓從古至今的秘密，一切的來龍去脈湧入她的大腦。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，不是現在。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希醫生……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眾魂的意志在影響你，他們迫不及待地想讓你接受他們的選擇。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想理解……她的情感。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你需要直面她。我們都需要。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "是的，阿米婭。;我們一起。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line374", "option2": "line374"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道的。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了眾魂之外……博士、凱爾希醫生、W小姐的心聲都很清晰。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一般敢用源石技藝窺探我的想法的人，下場都不太好。", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是……哈，我打賭我們這幾個走到這裡的人，想法都差不多。", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "急迫，緊張，又飽含著期待。"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和死寂的過往回聲截然不同的，是屬於此時此刻的鮮活情感。"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一起上去吧，還差最後一點了。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我想想看，這層透明的天花板該怎麼拆？", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她已經告訴了我。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "懸在他們頭頂的，黑暗中的眼睛。"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個菱形。"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既像是黑暗中僅有的光源，又彷彿是吞噬了萬物光華的罪魁禍首——"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g20_babeltop_ex3", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭抬起頭。"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眾魂之間的每一個魔王抬起頭。"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭向菱形伸出手去。"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眾魂之間的每一個魔王都伸出手去。"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g12_babeltop_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是第一位魔王留給我的唯一的言語——"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“如黑夜般籠罩我們的石頭，它是我們的苦難，更是一種希望。”"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們恰是為了希望而來。"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這一刻，“遠逐者”“砌城匠”“青色怒火”……所有魔王都與我在一起。就連以勒什都再度拿起了他的法杖。"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們與我一同戰鬥。"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了同一個使命。"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "魔王的使命。"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲的未來，將在此揭曉。"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天與地，上與下，光明與黑暗，未來與過去——"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都在瞬間倒轉。"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在塔頂也是塔底，終點也是原點，阿米婭聽到了一聲嘆息。"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們等到你了……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……“魔王”。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}